Class House

  • java.lang.Object
    • House
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HouseBuilder
    public class House
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a house in which the appliances will operate and have its usage recorded by the meters for electricity and water.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      House()
      Constructor creates and initialises two types of meters, one for electric and another for water.
      House​(Meter electricMeter, Meter waterMeter)
      Overloaded constructor with two parameters for two meters should the client want to use their own meters
